CRYSTAL APPLIED said unconsolidated sales
in December fell 83.24% to NT$44,294,000 from NT$264,220,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  12/2011          12/2010
Sales             44,294          264,220    
YOY%             -83.24%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,948,150        2,207,506   
YOY%             -11.75% 
